<L>__{exterior outskirts of ramelle dawn}
<A>__{first light. lovely. dew shimmers. a ground fog drifts. a sound. louder. and louder. a german tiger tank rumbles toward the village.}
<L>__{exterior bridge ramelle dawn}
<A>__{all are awake. at their positions. waiting.}
<C>__{miller}
<D>__{hears the faint distant rumble of the tank. barely has time to react. sees:}
<B>__{the germans advancing again}
<C>__{miller}
<D>__{here they come.}
