<D>__{shoves the final shell into the breech of the eighty eight. pats ryan on the back. grabs a satchel charge.}
<A>__{runs down the bridge. right toward the two advancing tanks.}
<C>__{ryan}
<D>__{fires the eighty eight.}
<B>__{destroying the third tank.}
<C>__{miller}
<D>__{races through the debris. trailed by bullets.}
<C>__{reiben}
<D>__{with the machine gun. covers miller. keeping most of the german infantry down.}
