<B>__{the last german tank}
<A>__{turret spins. turning toward the fast approaching miller. ready to blow him to bits.}
<C>__{miller}
<D>__{is almost there. he arms the satchel charge.}
<A>__{the tiger's machine guns opens up on him.}
<B>__{blasts a trail of bullets}
